history.content:
Late post, but the info session for the Game Design and Development Decal is tonight from 7-8:30PM PST!  This is a great decal for artists and programmers of all levels to get involved with developing video games.  If you're interested in learning more, come to the info session. I hope to see some of you guys there!

Here's the facebook event: https://www.facebook.com/events/1468921663313123/
